Regarding the Androzip, which was recommended by the seeder, I personally prefer the "ASTRO File Manager" - advanced file manager with many extra features. By the way it's completely free and can be downloaded from the Market or from http://www.freewarelovers.com/android/app/astro-file-manager if you cannot access Market for whatever reason.
